    "description": "P.E.P Is an online 8 Player PvEvP game set in a zombie filled coastal United States City. <br>Loot, Upgrade, and kill your way through the city in 5 Gamemodes. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164080/extras/85fc28fab060f9b4ccc777a72d5fceb8.poster.avif?t=1754318749\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164080/extras/85fc28fab060f9b4ccc777a72d5fceb8.webm?t=1754318749\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164080/extras/85fc28fab060f9b4ccc777a72d5fceb8.mp4?t=1754318749\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Play Extraction to explore the city and fight both AI/Player zombies, using an arsenal of unique weapons/throwables as you attempt to reach your extraction site. <br>Or play TDM, Gun Game, Or Dog Tags to fight other Human Survivors of the zombie outbreak as AI zombie's horde attack both teams!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164080/extras/e864c63b52d99ea1830cd8e06b5d5688.poster.avif?t=1754318749\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164080/extras/e864c63b52d99ea1830cd8e06b5d5688.webm?t=1754318749\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164080/extras/e864c63b52d99ea1830cd8e06b5d5688.mp4?t=1754318749\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Or Play as a team against infinite waves of zombie and special creatures in the new &quot;Horde&quot; mode! Buy unique upgrade to your character to survive as long as possible.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164080/extras/86ee339ecf3ec07b791f5a4fc44bcc45.poster.avif?t=1754318749\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164080/extras/86ee339ecf3ec07b791f5a4fc44bcc45.webm?t=1754318749\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164080/extras/86ee339ecf3ec07b791f5a4fc44bcc45.mp4?t=1754318749\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Use An Arsenal Of unique Gadgets to call in Cluster Strikes, Mounted Turrets, Vehicles, and more! <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164080/extras/3dab49785013d0dd6a4aa7a41045e933.poster.avif?t=1754318749\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164080/extras/3dab49785013d0dd6a4aa7a41045e933.webm?t=1754318749\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164080/extras/3dab49785013d0dd6a4aa7a41045e933.mp4?t=1754318749\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
